{
  "3244040": {
    "name": "The Golden Horde: Survival",
    "steam_appid": 3244040,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/cf33075fee930324f9aadcf118be4009.poster.avif?t=1751572022\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/cf33075fee930324f9aadcf118be4009.webm?t=1751572022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/cf33075fee930324f9aadcf118be4009.mp4?t=1751572022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《金帐汗国：生存》是一款中世纪题材的第一人称和第三人称生存角色扮演游戏。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏将带你回到残酷而神秘的13世纪，强大的金帐汗国正迅速崛起。挣脱奴役，努力生存，建立自己的定居点，并领导一场反抗运动，在一个真实历史与幻想元素交织的世界里谱写传奇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/440cfd43e7c12384919a4a50a2644c60.poster.avif?t=1751572022\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/440cfd43e7c12384919a4a50a2644c60.webm?t=1751572022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/440cfd43e7c12384919a4a50a2644c60.mp4?t=1751572022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>加入其中一个派系，在残酷无情的中世纪世界中寻找盟友。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择你的道路：成为忠诚的支持者，或秘密的反叛者。为自由而战，领导对抗强大帝国的起义，改写你所处时代的历史。你的选择将决定你所在派系乃至整个世界的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/5f6fe1c0c5a0847caad3c7f5f46c14b2.poster.avif?t=1751572022\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/5f6fe1c0c5a0847caad3c7f5f46c14b2.webm?t=1751572022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/5f6fe1c0c5a0847caad3c7f5f46c14b2.mp4?t=1751572022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>踏上充满神秘洞穴和危险地下城的开放世界冒险之旅。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索隐秘的角落，寻找宝藏，与敌人战斗以解放被奴役的人们。每拯救一条生命，你就离建立一个全新自由的世界更近一步！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/006b8bf2f25fbc81fbaa7668bf67850f.poster.avif?t=1751572022\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/006b8bf2f25fbc81fbaa7668bf67850f.webm?t=1751572022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/006b8bf2f25fbc81fbaa7668bf67850f.mp4?t=1751572022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在中世纪世界生存是终极的耐力考验！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小心致命的疾病，避免毒蛇咬伤和意外事故。保护好自己的身体——失去一条肢体可能是致命的。战胜饥饿和干渴，躲避奴役的威胁，为每一天的生存而战斗。在这里，每一步可能都是你最后的一步，每个决定都是生死攸关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/4d71e3267fb41fb639e1e8f276e6deb3.poster.avif?t=1751572022\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/4d71e3267fb41fb639e1e8f276e6deb3.webm?t=1751572022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/4d71e3267fb41fb639e1e8f276e6deb3.mp4?t=1751572022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸于古老时代，用你自己的双手铸就命运。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造舒适的蒙古包，将荒芜之地转变为繁荣的村落。探索广阔的领土，寻找稀有资源，打造武器与工具，迎接严酷中世纪生活的挑战。你的故事将成为关于生存、工艺和勇气的传奇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/e36766175f61929f63733202252ed3aa.poster.avif?t=1751572022\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/e36766175f61929f63733202252ed3aa.webm?t=1751572022\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244040/extras/e36766175f61929f63733202252ed3aa.mp4?t=1751572022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
